-- Venezuela’s Chavez Closing Post Operative Phase, Maduro Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2013-01-24T02:59:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-24/venezuela-s-chavez-closing-post-operative-phase-maduro-says.html
President Hugo Chavez is closing a
post-operative “cycle” after a fourth surgery for an
undisclosed cancer, Venezuelan Vice President Nicolas Maduro
said.  Maduro, speaking in an interview on Russian state
broadcaster RT, said Chavez was living the “best moment” of
his post-operative phase.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
